# Fibonacci

Recursion + parameters + If + comparison + arithmetic + user-defined fn call.

```scalascript
def fib(n: Long): Long =
  if (n < 2) n
  else fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)

@main def run(): Unit =
  println(fib(10))
```

Build and run:

```bash
ssc build-rust fib.ssc
./fib                          # → 55
```
